# Web3Forms — for the contact form ("LET'S WORK TOGETHER")
# Get a free access key at https://web3forms.com (takes 2 minutes):
#   1. Go to https://web3forms.com
#   2. Enter the email where you want to receive submissions
#   3. Verify the email (one-time)
#   4. Copy the access key shown on the page
#   5. Copy this file to .env.local (which is gitignored)
#   6. Paste your key below
#   7. Restart `npm run dev`
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
